## Step 3 — Add cancellation support (if requested)

### In the create workflow's Run method

```go
cancellationHandler := common.NewWorkflowCancellationHandler(
	ctx,
	"cancel-<resource>-create",
	params.ResourceUUID,
	params.ResourceName,
)

rollbackMgr := common.NewRollbackManager()

// Before each major activity, check cancellation
if err := cancellationHandler.CheckCancellation(ctx); err != nil {
	rollbackMgr.Execute(ctx)
	return nil, vsaerrors.ExtractCustomError(err)
}

// After each activity that creates a resource, register its rollback
rollbackMgr.AddActivity(ctx, activityStruct.DeleteMethod, deleteArgs...)
```

### In the delete workflow

```go
err := common.HandleCancellationInDeleteWorkflow(
	ctx,
	"cancel-<resource>-create",
	createJobID,
	temporal,
)
```

