## Step 4 — Register in worker

Add registration to `worker/main.go` in `RegisterCustomerWorkflowsAndActivities`:

```go
// Workflow registration
worker.RegisterWorkflow(workflows.<Resource><Operation>Workflow)

// Activity registration
worker.RegisterActivity(&activities.<Resource><Operation>Activity{SE: dbcon})
```

If the workflow is a background task, register in `RegisterBackgroundWorkflowsAndActivities` instead.

