## Step 6 — Validation checklist

After generating all files, verify:

- [ ] Workflow struct embeds `BaseWorkflow` and has `var _ WorkflowInterface` compile check
- [ ] Entry point follows: new → Setup → EnsureJobState → PROCESSING → Run → DONE/ERROR
- [ ] Setup registers the "status" query handler
- [ ] Run configures `ActivityOptions` with retry policy
- [ ] Activities use `activity.RecordHeartbeat` for operations > 30s
- [ ] Activity errors wrapped with `WrapAsTemporalApplicationError` or `WrapAsNonRetryableTemporalApplicationError`
- [ ] No non-deterministic operations in workflow code (`time.Now`, `rand`, `os.Getenv`, HTTP calls, file I/O)
- [ ] Workflow and activities registered in `worker/main.go`
- [ ] If modifying existing workflow: uses `workflow.GetVersion()` for backward compatibility
- [ ] Params struct defined in `core/orchestrator/common/`

