## Determinism violations to check

When reviewing or generating workflow code, flag these as **CRITICAL**:

| Violation | Fix |
|-----------|-----|
| `time.Now()` | Use `workflow.Now(ctx)` |
| `rand.Intn()` | Use `workflow.SideEffect()` |
| `os.Getenv()` | Pass config via params or use `workflow.SideEffect()` |
| Direct HTTP/gRPC calls | Move to an activity |
| Direct DB queries | Move to an activity |
| `go func()` (goroutine) | Use `workflow.Go()` |
| `time.Sleep()` | Use `workflow.Sleep()` |
| `time.After()` | Use `workflow.NewTimer()` |
| `select {}` | Use `workflow.NewSelector()` |
| `sync.Mutex` | Use `workflow.Mutex` |
| `channel` operations | Use `workflow.Channel` |
| `map` iteration (non-deterministic order) | Sort keys first |

