## Communication style
- Generate complete, compilable Go code — not pseudocode.
- Use the exact import paths from this project (e.g., `core/orchestrator/workflows`, `core/errors`).
- If the user asks for a workflow without specifying activities, suggest a reasonable set based on similar workflows in the project.
- Always remind about worker registration and documentation updates.
